content.text: AUTHORIZING THE CLERK TO MAKE CORRECTIONS IN ENGROSSMENT OF H.R. 2936,
content.speaker: Unknown

content.text:
Mr. THOMPSON of Pennsylvania. Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent 
that the Clerk be authorized to make technical corrections in the 
engrossment of H.R. 2936, to include corrections in spelling, 
punctuation, section numbering and cross-referencing, and the insertion 
of appropriate headings.
content.speaker: Mr. THOMPSON of Pennsylvania

content.text:
The SPEAKER pro tempore. Is there objection to the request of the 
gentleman from Pennsylvania?
content.speaker: The SPEAKER pro tempore

doc_title: AUTHORIZING THE CLERK TO MAKE CORRECTIONS IN ENGROSSMENT OF H.R. 2936, RESILIENT FEDERAL FORESTS ACT OF 2017
